TitleEnglish: Nintama Rantaro the Movie: The Dokutake Ninja Team's Strongest Strategist
SummaryEnglish: Rantaro, Kirimaru and Shinbei are far from excellent ninjas. As they embark on their training at ninja school, they are joined by their ironic friends, ninja masters, and older ninja idol trainees. All the incredible mistakes and confusion throughout your training lay the groundwork for a lot of fun and entertainment.
